## 8. Hardware Summary

{% table %}
- Component
- Spec
---
- MCU
- ESP32-S3 (Xtensa LX7 dual-core, 240 MHz)
---
- Sensors
- 5× flex sensors, resistive divider to ADC1
---
- ADC
- 12-bit, ADC1_CH0–CH4 (GPIO 1–5), 12dB attenuation
---
- Sampling rate
- 10 Hz (100 ms loop)
---
- Flash storage
- SPIFFS partition labelled `storage` — dataset.bin binary
---
- Connectivity
- USB-Serial (115200 baud) + BLE 5.0 NUS (NimBLE)
---
- Pull config
- GPIO_PULLDOWN_ONLY on all sensor GPIOs
{% /table %}

